data.description: Let the sun power your lifestyle in this home equipped with state-of-the-art solar technology. While solar is a huge perk to this home the location gets you close to all the amazing shopping and restaurants Chisolm Creek has to offer. Bring your vision and turn this home into everything you want. Seize the opportunity to add your personal touch while enjoying the benefit of existing solar panels!
